---
import Base from '~/layouts/Base.astro';
import { url } from '~/lib/url';
---
<Base title="Our farm — FreshMangoes" description="The story of our family orchard in Srinivasapur, Karnataka — twenty years of patient mango farming.">
  <section class="relative bg-[color:var(--color-leaf-700)] text-[color:var(--color-cream)]">
    <div class="container-x py-24 lg:py-32">
      <p class="eyebrow !text-[color:var(--color-saffron-300)] mb-4">Our Farm</p>
      <h1 class="display text-5xl md:text-7xl max-w-3xl leading-[1.02]">
        A family orchard, between Kolar and Chintamani.
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-x py-20 grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.2fr] gap-12">
    <div class="display text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight">
      "Patience is the most important ingredient. The mango decides when it's ready — we just listen."
      <p class="text-base font-sans not-italic opacity-70 mt-6">— our grandfather, 2005</p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-5 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed opacity-90">
      <p>
        In 2005, our family planted the first hundred grafted Alphonso saplings on a quiet patch of
        land in Srinivasapur, where the red soil holds the heat just so and the night air keeps
        the mangoes sweet.
      </p>
      <p>
        Two decades on, the orchard has grown — Banganpalli for the season's first sweetness,
        Mallika for its perfume, Totapuri for the slow-cooked summer kitchen, and our heirloom
        Sendura that you won't find in many markets. Every tree has a name.
      </p>
      <p>
        We don't gas. We don't ship hard. We pluck at the precise moment a mango asks to be plucked,
        cushion it in paper shavings, and put it on a truck the same day. From our hand to yours,
        usually in 24–48 hours.
      </p>
      <p>
        FreshMangoes is the small online side of a family business — built so you can taste what we taste,
        at the breakfast table.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-[color:var(--color-saffron-50)]">
    <div class="container-x py-16 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
      <div>
        <div class="display text-6xl">2005</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm opacity-70 uppercase tracking-wider">First trees</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="display text-6xl">10</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm opacity-70 uppercase tracking-wider">Mango varieties</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="display text-6xl">24h</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm opacity-70 uppercase tracking-wider">From farm to box</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-x py-20 text-center">
    <h2 class="display text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4">Taste the season.</h2>
    <p class="opacity-70 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">Most varieties peak between April and July. Shop now to claim yours from this year's harvest.</p>
    <a href={url('/shop')} class="btn btn-saffron">Browse the harvest →</a>
  </section>
</Base>
